text: That's My Girl is an R&B; song by Fifth Harmony. It was released on September 27, 2016. It is from their second studio album, 7/27. The lyrics speak of feminism and female empowerment. It has reached the Top 10 in Belgium and New Zealand. https://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=Fifth+Harmony&titel;=That%27s+My+Girl&cat;=s ==References== Category:R&B; songs Category:2016 songs
title: That's My Girl
